Human Resource Manager
Offshore Recruitment Services
UAE
Posted on: 29 Apr 2014
THE ROLE
Expand all
Purpose of the job:
•To enhance the performance of Company’s personnel, develop and recognize talent and keep within the legal parameters of the country of origin
• The timely recruitment of skilled personnel capable of making a significant contribution to the business unit and group
• Monitor retention levels for skilled managers and staff within each business function.
• Achievement of periodic appraisals for all staff (PMS); at a minimum of once annually and provide the necessary support and guidance where required.
• Notes and comments on internal and external audit reports.
• The motivation, development and general performance of the HR Team.
REQUIREMENTS
Qualifications & Experience:
•	Qualified in a recognized Human Resources discipline to a minimum standard of BA Degree
•	 Charted Member of the CIPD, including relevant post qualification experience.
•	Proficiency in HR practices that includes, payroll, policy development and deployment, organizational design, job evaluation, performance management, recruitment, communication, employee engagement and retention strategies.
•	Management experience including budgeting, forecasting, monthly reporting
•	Proven ability for implementing and monitoring MIS information
•	Leadership and staff management experience
•	Knowledge of the local labour laws
•	 IT literacy
•	To be passionate about SAS’s International’s aims and ethos.
ABOUT THE COMPANY
Offshore Recruitment Services specialise in the recruitment of in all aspects of offshore vacancies for all levels of permanent, temporary and contract positions.
Whether a client is searching for a highly skilled candidate, looking to head hunt a specific individual, a team of contractors for a project or management of gifted personnel, we are ready and have a proven track record of meeting such requirements.
Offshore Recruitment Services was formed with the specific aim of providing a quality service to link key candidates to our clients. We find the right people for your business.
